OL,3,CPolice officer found guilty of
OL,4,Csexually abusing a child
OL,6,FA Gwent police officer has been found
OL,7,Fguilty of five counts relating to the
OL,8,Fsexual abuse of a child.
OL,10,FJohn Stringer, who's 42 and from
OL,11,FCardiff, had denied the accusations.
OL,13,FBut today, after just over a day of
OL,14,Fdeliberation, the jury returned guilty
OL,15,Fverdicts on all charges.
OL,17,FThey unanimously found Stringer guilty
OL,18,Fof two counts of sexual assault by
OL,19,Ftouching and one charge of causing or
OL,20,Finciting a child to engage in sexual
OL,21,Factivity.
