OL,3,CPolice officer found guilty of
OL,4,Csexually abusing a child
OL,6,FHe was also found guilty of a further
OL,7,Fcharge of causing or inciting a child
OL,8,Fto engage in sexual activity and one
OL,9,Fcharge of causing a child to watch a
OL,10,Fsexual act, by majorities of 11 to 1
OL,11,Fand 10 to 2 respectively.
OL,13,FJudge Daniel Williams thanked the jury
OL,14,Fof 9 men and 3 women and remanded
OL,15,FStringer in custody until sentencing
OL,16,Fon October 28th.
OL,18,FThe police constable is currently
OL,19,Fsuspended from his duties with the
OL,20,FGwent force.
