OL,6,FThe week-long trial at Cardiff Crown
OL,7,FCourt had centred on the evidence of a
OL,8,Fyoung female victim, who was aged
OL,9,Funder 13 at the time of the offences.
OL,11,FThe victim - who can't be named for
OL,12,Flegal reasons - told police that Mr
OL,13,FStringer had put a blanket over her
OL,14,Fwhile she was playing video games
OL,15,Fbefore touching her inappropriately.
OL,17,FShe also told officers how, on another
OL,18,Foccasion, the defendant had shown her
OL,19,Fa video of an adult woman performing a
OL,20,Fsex act, before telling her to act out
OL,21,Fwhat she'd seen.
