OL,6,FShe went on to describe how Stringer
OL,7,Fhad asked her what she'd learned in
OL,8,FSRE (Sex and Relationships Education)
OL,9,Fclasses, and that it would be "her
OL,10,Ffault" if her parents found out about
OL,11,Fwhat had happened and he got into
OL,12,Ftrouble.
OL,14,FHis behaviour made her feel "very
OL,15,Funcomfortable", she told officers.
OL,17,FThe court was told that the
OL,18,Fallegations related to the period of
OL,19,Ftime between December 2019 and July
OL,20,F2021.
